<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM6.4">
<l>nāṟṟicait tīrttaṅ koṇarntu naṉinalkip</l>
<l>pārppaṉac ciṭṭarkaḷ pallā reṭut tēttip</l>
<l>pūppuṉai kaṇṇip puṉitaṉō ṭeṉṟaṉṉaik</l>
<l>kāppunāṇ kaṭṭak kaṉākkaṇṭēṉ tōḻīnāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O friend! I dreamt that many learned brahmins blessed [me] in a loud voice,</l>
<l>bringing water from [all] four quarters and sprinkling [it] well,</l>
<l>and tied amulets [binding] me with the pure Lord</l>
<l>[who wears] garlands strung with flowers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
